echidna_deposit_completes().custom:invariant: Deposits of any value should always succeed unless `_to` = `address(0)` or `_isCreation` = `true`. All deposits, barring creation transactions and transactions sent to `address(0)`, should always succeed.

documentation.text:
@custom:invariant Deposits of any value should always succeed unless
 `_to` = `address(0)` or `_isCreation` = `true`.
 All deposits, barring creation transactions and transactions sent to `address(0)`,
 should always succeed.
